Subject: drm/exynos: rename s/HDMI_OVERLAY_NUMBER/MIXER_WIN_NR
Git-commit: a634dd54c05636a89a272e27e59118374065975e
Patch-mainline: v3.4-rc3

HDMI_OVERLAY_NUMBER is specific of mixer driver and be used "windows
layer" term in exynos user manaual, so rename it.

